text: Cantharus elegans is a species of sea snails in the family Pisaniidae, the true whelks. It is found in Panama and Mexico. == References == == External links == * * Cantharus elegans at Museum of Comparative Zoology - Harvard University * Cantharus elegans at conchology.be Category:Pisaniidae Category:Gastropods described in 1834 Category:Taxa named by Edward Griffith (zoologist) Category:Molluscs of Mexico Category:Fauna of Panama
title: Cantharus elegans
